description:
Serena`s Delphox is the evolved form of Serena`s Braixen. It evolved sometime before the events of the Lilycove City Pokémon Contest.
It participated in the Lilycove City Pokémon Contest with Serena`s Sylveon and Serena`s Pancham and they won the contest in a tie with Lisia.
name: Mafoxy (Serena)
